ze-full screen-capture\"><img width=\"930\" height=\"590\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-3.jpg\" alt=\"Compare Image\" class=\"wp-image-1794\" srcset=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-3.jpg 930w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-3-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-3-768x487.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-3-150x95.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px\" \/><figcaption><em>Set off-canvas as type in Theme Options<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Products Max Count<\/strong> option is to set the number of products that are able to show off in Compare page. If you input 4, then 4 products are displayed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full screen-capture\"><img width=\"930\" height=\"511\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-1.jpg\" alt=\"Compare Image\" class=\"wp-image-1792\" srcset=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-1.jpg 930w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-1-300x165.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-1-768x422.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/compare-1-150x82.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px\" \/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This is a function that is available to compare simil